Package PayrollProcessing

  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    Company
    Company class representing database of Employees.
    Controller
    Controller is the operational class for the JavaFX Payroll Processing GUI
    Date
    Date class represents String of Date object and implements the Java Interface Comparable.
    Employee
    Employee class implements the general employee of a Company.
    Fulltime
    Fulltime class extends the Employee class and includes specific data and operations to a full-time employee.
    Main
    Main used for launching the GUI
    Management
    Management class implements objects that inherit properties of the Fulltime class.
    Parttime
    Parttime extends Employee and includes specific data and operations for a Parttime Employee.
    Profile
    Profile class represents the identifying profile for employees.
